Cam::

After being cooped up in the base, she wanted to stay outside for a 
while.  She decided while Windlord was distracted with Rodimus, she 
took off into the woods and went into hiding. She used her camoflage 
skills to hide under the foliage and seem to disappear. She 
chuckled, "WOn't he be suprized. He'll be looking for a while. I'm 
good at hiding. Heh heh heh."
